quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,Sulletun minelﾂｴevveliyne
  56,40,Ve sulletun minelahiriyne
  56,41,Ve ashabuﾅ淒殃mali ma ishabuﾅ淒殃mali
  56,42,Fiy semumin ve hamiymin
  56,43,Ve zﾄｱllin min yahmumin
  56,44,La baridin ve la keriymin
  56,45,ﾄｰnnehum kanu kable zalike mutrefiyne
  56,46,Ve kanu yusﾄｱrrune ﾂｴalelhﾄｱnsilﾂｴazﾄｱymi
  56,47,Ve kanu yekulune eiza mitna ve kunna turaben ve ﾂｴﾄｱzamen einne lemebﾂｴusune
  56,48,Eve abaunelﾂｴevvelune
  56,49,Kul innelﾂｴevveliyne velﾂｴahﾄｱriyne
  56,50,Lemecmuﾂｴune ila miykati yevmin maﾂｴlumin
  56,51,Summe innekum eyyuheddallunelmukezzibune
  56,52,Leakilune min ﾅ歹cerin min zakkumin
  56,53,Femaliune minhelbutune
  56,54,Feﾅ歛ribune ﾂｴaleyhi minelhamiymi
  56,55,Feﾅ歛ribune ﾅ殷rbelhiymi
  56,56,Haza nuzuluhum yevmeddiyni
  56,57,Nahnu halaknakum felevla tusaddikune
  56,58,Efereeytum ma tumnune
  56,59,Eentum tahlukunehu em nahnulhalikune
  56,60,Nahnu kadderna beynekumulmevte ve ma nahnu bimesbukﾄｱyne
  56,61,ﾂｴAla en nubeddile emsalekum ve nunﾅ殃ekum fiy ma la taﾂｴlemune
  56,62,Ve lekad ﾂｴalimtumunneﾅ淞ｴetelﾂｴula felevla tezekkerune
  56,63,Efereeytum ma tahrusune
  56,64,Eeentum tezreﾂｴunehu em nahnuzzariﾂｴune
  56,65,Lev neﾅ歛ﾂｴu leceﾂｴalnahu hutamen fezaltum tefekkehune
  56,66,ﾄｰnna lemuﾄ殲emune
  56,67,Bel nahnu mahrumune
  56,68,Efereeytumulmaelleziy teﾅ殲ebune
  56,69,Eentum enzeltumuhu minelmizni em nahnulmunzilune
  56,70,Lev neﾅ歛ﾂｴu ceﾂｴalnahu ucacen felevla teﾅ殘urune
  56,71,Efereeytumunnarelletiy turune
  56,72,Eentum enﾅ歹ﾂｴtum ﾅ歹cereteha em nahnul munﾅ殃une
  56,73,Nahnu ceﾂｴalnaha tezkireten ve metaﾂｴan lilmukviyne
  56,74,Fesibbﾄｱh bismi rabbikelﾂｴazﾄｱymi